^I^I^I&nbsp;









JPO




^Ilabel




Short Jump if Parity Odd. Only 8 low bits of result are checked.
Set by CMP, SUB, ADD, TEST, AND, OR, XOR instructions.
Algorithm:


^Iif PF = 0 then jump


^I
^Iexample for emu8086 emulator:

   include 'emu8086.inc'
   ORG 100h
   MOV AL, 00000111b   ; AL = 7
   OR  AL, 0           ; just set flags.
   JPO label1
   PRINT 'parity even.'
   JMP exit
label1:
   PRINT 'parity odd.'
exit:
   RET



